{{- section("Welcome!") -}}
Welcome to our community, and if this is your first time playing this game, welcome to NationStates as well!

There is so much more to this game than just answering issues, and this guide should help you find something to your liking.

If you ever have any questions, feel free to reach out to any member of the Triune Circle, our regional leadership:
[list]{%- for luminarch in parameters.people.luminarchs -%}
[*][nation]{{ luminarch.nation }}[/nation] ([b][url=page=compose_telegram?tgto={{ luminarch.nation }}][font=nationstates][/font] Telegram[/url][/b] - [b]Discord[/b]: {{ luminarch.discord }})
{% endfor %}[*][nation]{{ parameters.people.aetherion.nation }}[/nation] ([b][url=page=compose_telegram?tgto={{ parameters.people.aetherion.nation }}][font=nationstates][/font] Telegram[/url][/b] - [b]Discord[/b]: {{ parameters.people.aetherion.discord }})[/list]

If you find this dispatch useful, consider [b]upvoting[/b] it by clicking the [b]up arrow[/b] at the top of the page!
{{- endsection() -}}
[/box]{{- divider() -}}[box][anchor=start][/anchor]
{{- section("Getting Started") -}}
First things first:
[list][*] [b]Block Recruitment Telegrams[/b]: [i]Your inbox is likely being spammed by recruitment telegrams asking you to move regions right now. Now that you've joined Starlight, you'll want to stop the spam.[/i]

Head over to [b][url=https://www.nationstates.net/page=tgsettings][font=nationstates][/font] Telegram Settings[/url][/b] and select [b]Block All[/b] under "Recruitment". Click "Update Filter" and you're all set.
[*] [b]Join the World Assembly:[/b] [i]This lets you vote on international resolutions, strengthen your nation's power and influence, join our regional roleplay, and become a citizen.[/i]
[list=1]
[*] Make sure your nation has a [url=https://www.nationstates.net/page=settings]valid email set[/url], and apply to join the [b][url=https://www.nationstates.net/page=un][font=nationstates][/font] World Assembly[/url][/b].
[*] Go to your email and confirm your World Assembly application.
[*] Once you're a World Assembly member, endorse [b][url=https://nationstates.net/nation=vintrel#endorse]Vintrel[/url][/b] and [b][url=https://nationstates.net/nation=kaidan#endorse]Kaidan[/url][/b] by clicking the [b]Endorse Nation[/b] button at the bottom of their nation page.
[/list]
[/list]
{{- endsection() -}}
[/box]{{- divider() -}}[box][anchor=todo][/anchor]
{{- section("Things to Do") -}}
We pride ourselves in having a wide variety of activities for our members to participate in. Click on the links for more information on how to join each of them!

[list][*] [b][url=#rp][font=nationstates][/font] Roleplay[/url][/b]: Join one of our three roleplays and write stories in a variety of settings with nations across the galaxy.
[*] [b][url=#social][font=nationstates][/font] Hang Out[/url][/b]: Meet our active, bubbly community and make new friends.
[*] [b][url=#cit][font=nationstates][/font] Citizenship[/url][/b]: Lets you vote in regional elections, join the government, and take part in our legislature.
[*] [b][url=#mil][font=nationstates][/font] Galactic Armada[/url][/b]: Join our regional military to protect innocent regions from invader forces and strike back against bigoted regions.
[*] As a citizen, you will be able to participate in the following ministries:
[list][*] [b][url=#rec][font=nationstates][/font] Recruitment[/url][/b]: Help our wonderful community find new members.
[*] [b][url=#cult][font=nationstates][/font] Culture[/url][/b]: Plan and host exciting events, bringing the community together.
[*] [b][url=#game][font=nationstates][/font] Gameside[/url][/b]: Welcome new members, bolster on-site activity and drive engagement.
[*] [b][url=#media][font=nationstates][/font] Media[/url][/b]: Help write our regional newspaper, the Voice of the Stars.
[*] [b][url=#wa][font=nationstates][/font] World Assembly[/url][/b]: Analyze resolutions, craft voting recommendations, and create proposals of your own.
[*] [b][url=#fa][font=nationstates][/font] Foreign Affairs[/url][/b]: Meet friends from regions abroad and keep them in touch with what's happening here.
[/list]
[/list]
{{- endsection() -}}
[/box]{{- divider() -}}[box][anchor=rp][/anchor]
{{- section("Roleplay Opportunities") -}}
We have three different roleplay settings for you to dive into and jump into stories with both new and established roleplayers:
[list][*]🌌 [b]Celestara[/b], a sci-fi space roleplay set in an expansive galaxy of our own.
[*]👑 [b]Dawnbreak[/b], a fantasy roleplay set in the 1400s full of magical adventures. 
[*]🌍 [b]Nebulon[/b], a near future roleplay set in 2100 in an Earth like solar system.[/list]

All of them only require World Assembly membership to join, you do not need to be in our regional Discord server.

You can read more about them and how to join in our roleplay portal dispatch:
https://www.nationstates.net/page=dispatch/id=2769410
{{- endsection() -}}
[/box]{{- divider() -}}[box][anchor=social][/anchor]
{{- section("Hang Out") -}}
We have an active community that will be delighted to meet you and chat!

There are two main avenues through which we hang out:
[list][*] The [b][url={{ parameters.urls.regions.starlight }}#rmb][font=nationstates][/font] Regional Message Board[/url][/b], NationStates's built-in chat platform, open to any member as well as friends from other regions.
[*]The [b][url={{ parameters.urls.discord }}][font=nationstates][/font] regional Discord server[/url][/b], where most government activity as well as more casual and live chat happens. Our Discord server is one of the most active out of any region so we highly recommend you join - if you don't have a Discord account, making one is entirely free![/list]
{{- endsection() -}}
[/box]{{- divider() -}}[box][anchor=cit][/anchor]
{{- section("Citizenship") -}}
Being a citizen (also known as Starborn) of Starlight lets you shape our region by getting involved in the regional government, elections and legislature!

Citizenship is not required to be a member of the region or participate in things like roleplay, but it is a good step to take to get involved further in the region. After obtaining citizenship, you'll be able to apply to any of our ministries, which give you many opportunities to contribute to regional government and bring your ideas.[/size]

[size=130][b]✧ Requirements[/b][/size]
[list][*]If your nation is not in the World Assembly, you should explain why it cannot be, outline your World Assembly status elsewhere, and provide sufficient justification for wanting to be a citizen, including what areas of the region you are planning to contribute to.[/list]

[size=130][b]✧ How to Join[/b][/size]
[list][b][url={{ parameters.urls.discord }}]Join our regional Discord server[/url][/b] and fill out the form in [b][url=https://discord.com/channels/1299450621044330616/1494360172536004628/1494360172536004628]the Citizenship thread[/url][/b].[/list]
[/box]{{- divider() -}}[box][anchor=mil][/anchor]
{{- section("Military") -}}
The Galactic Armada, our defender military, works to protect innocent regions from invader forces, as well as invade fascist and undesirable regions ourselves.

Military gameplay is one of the most dynamic activities you can find on NationStates. No matter your level of experience, even if you've never done it before, our commanders will quickly get you up to speed on the mechanics needed so you, too, can become an elite defender![/size]

[size=130][b]✧ Requirements[/b][/size]
[list][*]You must not be currently enlisted in any other regional military.[/list]

[size=130][b]✧ How to Join[/b][/size]
[list][b][url={{ parameters.urls.discord }}]Join our regional Discord server[/url][/b] and fill out the form in [b][url=https://discord.com/channels/1299450621044330616/1494359827927928942/1494359827927928942]the Galactic Armada thread[/url][/b].[/list]

[size=130][b]✧ More Information[/b][/size]
https://www.nationstates.net/page=dispatch/id=2580677
[/box]{{- divider() -}}[box][anchor=rec][/anchor]
{{- section("Recruitment") -}}
Recruitment is a vital activity to maintain the health of our community and bring in new faces.

As a recruiter, you'll use our incredibly intuitive bot, Vanille, to help you send telegrams to new nations and invite them to our community. It is a very commitment-free task - even doing it a few minutes per day helps massively.[/size]

[size=130][b]✧ Requirements[/b][/size]
[list][*] Be a [b][url=#cit]citizen[/url][/b] of the region.[/list]

[size=130][b]✧ How to Join[/b][/size]
[list][b][url={{ parameters.urls.discord }}]Join our regional Discord server[/url][/b] and fill out the form in [b][url=https://discord.com/channels/1299450621044330616/1494359708486860830/1494359708486860830]the Recruitment thread[/url][/b].[/list]

[size=130][b]✧ More Information[/b][/size]
https://www.nationstates.net/page=dispatch/id=2770771
[/box]{{- divider() -}}[box][anchor=cult][/anchor]
{{- section("Ministry of Culture") -}}
The Ministry of Culture is tasked with planning and host exciting events to bring the community together.

As a member of the Ministry of Culture, you will help plan events, watch parties, games, contests, etc. to keep people entertained![/size]

[size=130][b]✧ Requirements[/b][/size]
[list][*] Be a [b][url=#cit]citizen[/url][/b] of the region.[/list]

[size=130][b]✧ How to Join[/b][/size]
[list][b][url={{ parameters.urls.discord }}]Join our regional Discord server[/url][/b] and fill out the form in [b][url=https://discord.com/channels/1299450621044330616/1494358985573404792/1494358985573404792]the Ministry of Culture thread[/url][/b].[/list]
[/box]{{- divider() -}}[box][anchor=game][/anchor]
{{- section("Ministry of Gameside") -}}
The Ministry of Gameside is tasked with welcoming new members, bolstering on-site activity and driving engagement.

As a member of the Ministry of Gameside, you will help welcome new members and integrate them into our community, encourage and drive regional activity on NationStates, especially on the regional message board, and post things like polls and questions of the day.[/size]

[size=130][b]✧ Requirements[/b][/size]
[list][*] Be a [b][url=#cit]citizen[/url][/b] of the region.[/list]

[size=130][b]✧ How to Join[/b][/size]
[list][b][url={{ parameters.urls.discord }}]Join our regional Discord server[/url][/b] and fill out the form in [b][url=https://discord.com/channels/1299450621044330616/1494359304591904970/1494359304591904970]the Ministry of Gameside thread[/url][/b].[/list]
[/box]{{- divider() -}}[box][anchor=media][/anchor]
{{- section("Ministry of Media") -}}
The Ministry of Media helps keep our members informed through regular publications of our regional newspaper, the Voice of the Stars.

As a member, you will help write articles and edit others' to make this publication as rich, high-quality and entertaining as possible.[/size]

[size=130][b]✧ Requirements[/b][/size]
[list][*] Be a [b][url=#cit]citizen[/url][/b] of the region.[/list]

[size=130][b]✧ How to Join[/b][/size]
[list][b][url={{ parameters.urls.discord }}]Join our regional Discord server[/url][/b] and fill out the form in [b][url=https://discord.com/channels/1299450621044330616/1494359141517361193/1494359141517361193]the Ministry of Media thread[/url][/b].[/list]
[/box]{{- divider() -}}[box][anchor=wa][/anchor]
{{- section("Ministry of World Assembly Affairs") -}}
The Ministry of WA Affairs writes voting recommendations for World Assembly resolutions and helps Starborn write their own proposals so that they have the best chance at success.

As a member, you'll help out in writing the aforementioned voting recommendations, our monthly World Assembly newsletter (The Intergalactic), and will be able to discuss and organize World Assembly projects with experienced authors.[/size]

[size=130][b]✧ Requirements[/b][/size]
[list][*] Be a [b][url=#cit]citizen[/url][/b] of the region.[/list]

[size=130][b]✧ How to Join[/b][/size]
[list][b][url={{ parameters.urls.discord }}]Join our regional Discord server[/url][/b] and fill out the form in [b][url=https://discord.com/channels/1299450621044330616/1494359486704386169/1494359486704386169]the Ministry of WA Affairs thread[/url][/b].[/list]
[/box]{{- divider() -}}[box][anchor=fa][/anchor]
{{- section("Ministry of Foreign Affairs") -}}
As part of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs, ambassadors let us know what happens in other regions and broadcast our own news to them.

As an ambassador, your main task will be to relay news updates to a region we're friends or allies with, as well as occasionally chat and be a friendly presence there! It is a great opportunity to get to know people in other regions and the wider NationStates world.[/size]

[size=130][b]✧ Requirements[/b][/size]
[list][*] Be a [b][url=#cit]citizen[/url][/b] of the region.[/list]

[size=130][b]✧ How to Join[/b][/size]
[list][b][url={{ parameters.urls.discord }}]Join our regional Discord server[/url][/b] and fill out the form in [b][url=https://discord.com/channels/1299450621044330616/1494359593399353395/1494359593399353395]the Ministry of Foreign Affairs thread[/url][/b].[/list]

[size=130][b]✧ More Information[/b][/size]
https://www.nationstates.net/page=dispatch/id=2599372[/box]

[i]This dispatch is updated automatically.[/i]
